Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:02:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hawk-Eye Mihawk! The Great\NSwordsman Zoro Falls on the Sea"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ugh...\N--What'd you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami ran off with the Going Merry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened just a moment ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Big Sis Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking at wanted posters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're impressive as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've set your eyes\Non a big bounty pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Arlong is the one pirate\Nthat you shouldn't go after.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear he's super terrifyingly strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept himself quiet\Nand out of sight for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he started going\Nwild again recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's hard to give up on that\N20-million berry bounty, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's so strong that\Nthere's a shred of possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that even we may be killed by a hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm, I'm sorry, but could you\Nturn around? I want to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change? Here? Now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True to her looks, she's so bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't hurt if we take\Na quick peek, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing? Of course, business!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a thief that only targets\Npirates. I'll take this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that I became a member.\NI just joined forces with them. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only spent a short time with Luffy\Nand the others, but I had lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tell them...\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that if we're linked\Nby fate, we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! We'll be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were more or less\Nasked to watch the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how she took the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! She's making\Nthis crisis worse for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya gave that ship to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I can still see it!\NIt's the Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Usopp! Leave right away!\NTake that ship and follow Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it.\NJust give that ship to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need of going after that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept anyone\Nbut her as our navigator!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right...\NWhat a high-maintenance captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Usopp, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh? Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big Bro Zoro, the ship is ready!\N--Big Bro Zoro, the ship is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go since I haven't settled\Nanything at this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.\NThe situation here isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? What the hell just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's been split into two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg! It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the man who destroyed our fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th... That man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He followed us here... to kill us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk-Eye Mihawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk-Eye Mihawk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's strongest man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the man who sank Krieg's\N50 ships on his own in the Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the one who destroyed\NKrieg's ship just now is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he looks just like\Nan ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like he\Nhas any special weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His weapon is on his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That... can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really slice up that large\Nsailing ship using that sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the master swordsman Hawk-Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the man who stands above all\Nother swordsmen in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd be\Nable to see him this soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally... time to fulfill my promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You son of a bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What grudge do you\Nhave to come after us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just killing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:08:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?! Don't mock us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I aimed straight for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He averted them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gently changed\Nthe course of the bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using the point of his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three swords... Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a sword\Nmoved so gently...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no strength in\Nswordplay based only on force.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you use that sword to\Nslice up this ship as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You're the strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came out to sea to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To become the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph... How foolish...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got spare time,\Nright? Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This guy is Zoro! Roronoa Zoro\Nof the Three Swords Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a pirate hunter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this isn't good, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry will\Nbe out of sight soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight? Hmph! How pitiful, weak one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are a competent\Nenough swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be able to see\Nthe disparity in our abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even before we cross swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it your courage or ignorance that\Ncauses you to turn your sword on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's also because of a\Npromise I made to a dear friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk-Eye Mihawk,\Nthe world's strongest swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the pirate hunter Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of fight will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There can't possibly be anyone\Nwho can defeat Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro is the strongest already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the meaning of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no beast that goes all\Nout when hunting a rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're a swordsman who's\Nearned a bit of a name for himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this sea, the East Blue, is the\Nweakest among the four seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't carry any\Nsmaller sharp instrument than this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough making fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better not regret it when I kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frog in the well...\NKnow how big the world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oni... Giri!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... Big Bro's Oni Giri was stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a big technique that never\Nfails to blow any enemy away was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't move them! What did he do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one has ever seen\Nthrough this technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he stopped it using a toy like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our abilities are this far apart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be right!\NThere's no way that it's this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's strongest can't be this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening,\Nright, Big Bro?! Get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be this far apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What ferocity your swordplay has...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking Zoro's Three Swords Style\Nattacks with such a small knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monster even beyond\Nthe monstrous Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't pursue\Nswordsmanship all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be dealt with by a toy like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky, Zoro. You're a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be the world's\Ngreatest swordsman, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only... If only I had been born a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be whining like\Nthat after you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair! You're my goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, one of us will be\Nthe world's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's a promise!\N--It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To become the world's strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm going to get\Nstronger for her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the world's greatest swordsman\Nso that my name will reach heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:14:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised her... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only to defeat this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you bear on your shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you desire once you've\Nobtained power, weak one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called Big Bro a\Nweak one? You cross bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you a lesson! He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Yosaku! Johnny!\NDon't intervene!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!\NThe world's greatest swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates would need\Nno less than that on his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just going to\Nlet me pierce your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you withdrawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I withdrew even a step,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like those various\Nimportant things such as pledges
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and promises in the\Npast will be shattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I won't be able to come\Nback to where I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's what defeat is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, all the more reason\NI can't withdraw...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you'll die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a strong heart!\NSo he chooses death over defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! State your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen anyone like you\Nin a while, strong one. Thus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as a swordsman's courtesy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sink you using the world's\Nstrongest black sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He took it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the sword that sliced up the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this'll be the last hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be the world's strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or death?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! That's enough! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Swords Style Secret Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:16:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Thousand Worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined I'd ever lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the power\Nof the world's strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scars on the back are\Na swordsman's shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't live so hastily, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big Bro!!\N--Big Bro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I decided to become\Nthe strongest swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to devote my life to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy! His opponent\Nis the real world's strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How it'd turn out was clear. He should\Ngive up his ambition rather than die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.63,0:18:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be easy...\Nto give up your ambition, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the power of the Grand Line...\Nthe power of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think the pirate hunter Zoro\Nis as helpless as a new-born baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, damn you... Damn you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big Bro!!\N--Big Bro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that brat... has the\Npower of a devil fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that young\Nswordsman's comrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:19:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also impressed me for\Nwatching it to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I didn't kill that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Big Bro! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry up and get\Nhim up on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is medicine! Throw it over him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early for you to die.\NMy name is Dracule Mihawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn about yourself!\NLearn about the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And become strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many years it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will hold this seat of\Nthe strongest and wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surpass this sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to surpass me! Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Big Bro, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that he got Hawk-Eye\NMihawk to say this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, what is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be even harder than surpassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know when\NI haven't done it yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big Bro!\N--Big Bro! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need no less than the world's\Ngreatest swordsman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Please don't talk any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I will not be defeated ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the day I defeat him\Nand become a master swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never... be defeated!\NGot any problems with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good team.\NI want to see you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hawk-Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come to take my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the life of the East\NBlue's ruler, Don Krieg?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to, but I had enough fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going home to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have had enough,\Nbut I'm tired of getting beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to keep him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die before you leave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected...\Nhe never learns a lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:22:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! He escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.00,0:22:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! I'll leave Nami to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Zoro and I will\Nbring Nami back for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get that cook to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When all five of us\Nare reunited, let's go to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! We ran into some interference,\Nbut the real fight starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.36,0:22:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, can I stop doing\Nchores if I drive them away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:23:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Krieg and his pirates are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:23:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, what an\Nungrateful bunch they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.71,0:24:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when they were given food!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.48,0:24:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's another ungrateful one\Nwho took treasure and ran off...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't worry\Nabout it! Get some rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a weird guy came out...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.65,0:24:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fully armed with shields!\NOw, ow, ow! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.99,0:24:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Deadly Foot Technique Bursts Forth!\NSanji vs. the Invincible Pearl"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.66,0:24:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
